The paper deals with automatically annotating column types in web tables using knowledge base concepts and machine learning. This involves tasks related to databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
